import React from 'react';
import { Typography, Box, TextField, Button } from '@mui/material';

const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <Box id="contact" sx={{ p: 2 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>Contact</Typography>
      <form noValidate autoComplete="off">
        <TextField
          label="Name"
          variant="outlined"
          fullWidth
          margin="normal"
        />
        <TextField
          label="Email"
          variant="outlined"
          fullWidth
          margin="normal"
        />
        <TextField
          label="Message"
          variant="outlined"
          fullWidth
          margin="normal"
          multiline
          rows={4}
        />
        <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
          Send
        </Button>
      </form>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Contact;
